00:20:33,733 --> 00:20:37,357
And so publishers will at times re-theme games.

411
00:20:37,357 --> 00:20:40,580
This is one of our games that I've re-themed.

412
00:20:40,580 --> 00:20:42,842
It was pitched to us as a flower-themed game.

413
00:20:42,842 --> 00:20:46,485
So you were planting flowers, harvesting flowers, and making bouquets.

414
00:20:46,885 --> 00:20:49,647
Nothing wrong with flower themed games, there have been some that have done quite well,

