00:21:04,772 --> 00:21:09,015
Everybody at the table will get a resource matching the color that's facing them

421
00:21:09,015 --> 00:21:14,239
And I thought that sounded fascinating and wanted to play it. I played it loved it

422
00:21:14,239 --> 00:21:19,482
But wanted to look at rechanging the theme so I made this theme list prototype

423
00:21:19,482 --> 00:21:26,267
I use the paint shop or the photoshop paint bucket tool to color out all the flowers and just make a solid color

424
00:21:26,267 --> 00:21:27,428
abstract version and

425
00:21:28,909 --> 00:21:32,311
listen to what players, as they played, what they said about the game.

