00:21:32,311 --> 00:21:35,173
So, the mechanics would give them these feelings,

427
00:21:35,173 --> 00:21:37,955
simple and elegant, it's calming, it's delightful,

428
00:21:37,955 --> 00:21:40,196
relaxing to play, and flowing.

